{"tid":1895554,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警員確診個案再有37警列密切接觸者　須接受檢疫 (22:53)","createTime":"2020-02-24T15:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T15:55:47.000Z","uid":5195,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9267466cc4f1c4a2b801f6742ae304111a10d692","tid":1895554,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:11:07.000Z","msg":"就一名駐守北角警署的48歲男警員確診新型冠狀病毒，警方今（24日）回覆查詢表示，除了59名曾與確診者在一起聚餐的警務人員已入住檢疫中心接受檢疫，現時有另外37名警務人員被界定為密切接觸者。<br />\n<br />\n截至今晚7時，其中22名密切接觸者已入住位於駿洋邨的檢疫中心，6人正在家中隔離，準備入住檢疫中心接受檢疫；5人正等待衛生署進一步通知；3名出現病徵並在醫院接受治療的警務人員經初步測試，結果呈陰性反應；而一名被衛生署界定為密切接觸者前已離港的警務人員，將於今日回港接受檢疫。 <br />\n<br />\n警方表示高度關注事件，會繼續與衛生署保持密切聯繫，以作出適時的檢疫安排。"},{"pid":"e7ae0eaa6bec12f6e780b9b69cba2d336162a24c","tid":1895554,"uid":201751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:11:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警死全家</span>"},{"pid":"676cfd55d0c3f971b5fa234094182c7385d2c48c","tid":1895554,"uid":293677,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:12:29.000Z","msg":"最緊要人有事<br />\n3萬 THX<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pu46jkh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPu46jkh.jpg&h=19630c38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75f85ea461f24fec265ecc2d7a9719e65d4fb0ae","tid":1895554,"uid":41873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:15:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三萬THANKS</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3030478da4b86d970c630148e760a721f257c23a","tid":1895554,"uid":40356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:15:56.000Z","msg":"最緊要有事🙏🏻"},{"pid":"712f2501b4e6457acb2ec60bb109b0e60f10cecc","tid":1895554,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7ae0eaa6bec12f6e780b9b69cba2d336162a24c","tid":1895554,"uid":201751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:11:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font